https://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip
http://codeonhill.com/paperclip-and-imagemagick-for-images-in-rails/


make sure image magick is installed - sudo apt-get install imagemagick -y

gem "paperclip", "~> 5.0.0"

bundle install

rails g paperclip post image  [here post is the model you want to add image to. it create 'image' column to the post table/model]

go to the paperclip github page, quick start section - copy the Model example code and paste in your model.

ACTIVE ADMIN - 

TO add choose file button in active admin check out the code in portfolio/app/admin/post.rb


